All things are in "vendor" folder

Each module has "vinilla.json" settings file

"vinilla.json" has this structure.

{
    "vendor": "CodingLiki",
    "name": "module_name",
    "version": "",
    "repo_url": "",
    "author": "Author",
    "description": "",
    "site": "",
    "root_folder": "",
    "depends_on": [
        "first_dependency_url",
        "second_dependency_url"
    ]
}

Required fields are:
    vendor
    name
    version
    repo_url

If "name" is empty or equals "", then "module_name" sets to repository name:
    for example, for repository 'https://github.com/Shiro7/mqtt_server_php.git' module_name will be "mqtt_server_php"

If "root_folder" is empty or equals "", then "root_folder" sets to "/"

